Amurka dole ne a ninka kudi a fannin fasaha intelligence
Yayin da kasar Sin ta ƙara aiki a fannin intelligence, Amurka dole ne ta ninka kudaden da aka sadaukar da su don bincike a cikin wannan yanki, a cewar mai zuba jari da kuma gwani na Kai-Fu Lee, wanda ya yi aiki ga Google, Microsoft, da kuma Apple.
Wadannan bayanai sun zo ne bayan da 'yan jarida da dama na gwamnatin Amurka suka sanar da AI, yayin da babu wata dabarun AI na hukuma a Amurka.
A lokaci guda, kasar Sin ta gabatar da takardun takardun shaida a shekarar da ta gabata: tana shirin zama jagora a cikin sabuwar IA a cikin 2030.
"Zaɓi kuɗin bincike a fannin AI zai zama kyakkyawan farawa, saboda duk sauran ƙasashe suna da tsawon lokaci a kan Amurka, kuma muna neman babban bincike mai zuwa a cikin AI," in ji Lee.
Biyu kudi zai iya ninka da yiwuwar cewa na gaba mahimman mataki a cikin AI ya zo daga Amurka, ya ce Lee ga CNBC a cikin hira wannan mako.
Lee, wanda littafin "AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order" ya wallafa wannan watan ta Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, shi ne shugaban kasar Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin AI na kasar Sin, Face++.
A cikin 1980s, a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon, ya yi aiki a kan wani tsarin AI wanda ya doke mai kunnawa na Othello na Amurka mafi kyau. Daga nan ya shiga cikin ƙungiyar jagorancin Microsoft Reasearch kuma ya zama shugaban reshe na Google na China.
Lee ya riga ya halarci gasar fasaha da gwamnatin Amurka ta shirya, kamar Robotics Challenge na Defense Advanced Research Projects Agency, kuma ya tambayi lokacin da za a gudanar da gasar na gaba, don gano masu hangen nesa.
Lee ya ce, masu bincike na Amurka sau da yawa dole ne su yi aiki tukuru don samun kudi daga gwamnati.
"Ba kasar Sin ba ce ta dauki shugabannin jami'o'i ba, amma kamfanoni ne," in ji Lee.
A cikin 'yan shekarun nan, Facebook, Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha sun sanya manyan sunayen jami'a don aiki akan IA.
Lee ya kara da cewa canje-canje na manufofin gudun hijira na iya kuma tallafawa kokarin Amurka akan AI.
"Ina tsammanin dole ne a ba da katunan kore ta atomatik ga masu bincike a IA," in ji shi.
