Trump yakin a West Virginia (YouTube Channel)
Shugaban kasar Donald Trump ya fara taron yakin neman zabe a Welling, Virginia ta Yamma.
Sauran wurare, musamman a jihohi kamar Tennessee da Mississippi inda shugaban kasa ya shahara, an shirya.
Lokacin da aka dakatar da kuri'un tabbatar da matsayi a Kotun Koli, Trump yana neman tattara goyon baya ga zaben tsakiya na gaba kuma ya hana 'yan Jamhuriyar su rasa iko a majalisar a lokacin zaben a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne ake gudanar da taron Trump a Virginia ta Yamma da yamma kuma ta yaya ake kallon shi a kan layi?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, a Virginia ta Yamma, don karfe 19:00 (haskin gabas) da yamma a ranar Asabar 29 ga watan Satumba 2018.
Za ka iya bi shi a kasa online, live a YouTube.
Trump ya kamata yayi magana game da tambayoyin dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ake zargi da laifin cin zarafin jima'i, wanda ya faru a wannan makon. Zaɓin tabbatarwa na Kavanaugh a majalisar dattijai ya kamata a dawo har zuwa mako guda a lokacin binciken FBI.
Amma wannan jerin taron ya fi dacewa don taimakawa Jam'iyyar Republican su ci nasara a zaben Nuwamba.
A cewar Reuters, shugaban Arewacin Amirka ya bayyana haka a yakinsa cewa taro biyar na nufin "karfafa masu ba da gudummawa da masu goyon baya yayin da 'yan Jamhuriyar ke kokarin karewa da kuma fadada yawancin da suke riƙe a majalisar dattawa da kuma majalisar wakilai."
"Shugaban majalisar ya zama wani muhimmin abu na shirinsa wanda shugaban kasa zai je mafi yawan jihohi a farkon zaben da aka yi," in ji mai magana da yawun tawagar Trump, wanda ya ƙi a nada shi.
Dangane da West Virginia Metro News, taron yau da dare, wanda aka tsara a Wesbanco Arena na Wheeling, zai iya tattara magoya baya daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania, da kuma jawo hankalin kafofin watsa labarun daga Pittsburgh".
Asabar, zai zama na biyu a wata daya na Trump a Virginia ta Yamma, jihar da ya lashe a 2016 da fiye da 40 kashi.
Trump yayi kokarin taimakawa Patrick Morrisey, dan takarar jam'iyyar Republican a majalisar dattijai ta Virginia ta Yamma, wanda ke cikin binciken.
"Ba wata alama ce mai kyau ga Morrisey cewa shugaban kasa dole ne ya zo don kokarin sake fasa shi a cikin binciken," in ji Simon Haeder, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
