Palu shine babban birnin lardin Sulawesi na tsakiya, wanda ke kusa da bakin teku na yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, wanda aka kiyasta yawan jama'a 379 800 a cikin 2017.
Birnin ya yi bikin cika shekaru 40 lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka faru.
