Mahukunta na tarayya na New York sun nemi hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargin wanda ya kashe takwas a New York - hukuncin da ba a yi a wannan jihar ba saboda laifin tarayya tun 1953.
Saipov, mai shekaru 30, ya yi amfani da motar haya tare da Home Depot don kai hari a kan hanya mai hawa a kan West Side Highway, a Lower Manhattan, inda ya fadi a kan hanyarsa na matafiya da kuma mai bikewa a watan Oktoba na karshe.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, dole ne masu shari’a su kawo hujjar cewa Saipov ya kashe 'da gangan takwas' kuma ya sanya "da gangan" mummunan lahani, bisa ga sanarwar da ya yi niyyar neman hukuncin kisa da aka gabatar a gundumar Kudancin New York.
