Amurka yanzu ta rasa sau shida a kan ƙasashen Turai kuma ba ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder a Turai tun 1993.
Turai ta dawo da lakabin lokacin da kungiyar captain Danish Thomas Bjorn ta wuce maki 14.5 da ake buƙata don doke Amurka.
Tauraron Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya sami matsala a lokacin yawancin gasar, ya zura kwallonsa a cikin ruwa a cikin rami na 16 a 3, ya ba Francesco Molinari wasansa.
Dan wasan golf na Italiya Molinari ya yi kyau a duk zagaye, inda ya zama daya daga cikin 'yan wasan hudu da suka taɓa kai 5-0-0 tun tsarin wasan kwaikwayo na yanzu, wanda kaddamar da farko ya koma 1979.
A Amurka Jordan Spieth ya kori 5 zuwa 4 daga cikin 'yan wasa mafi kyau a ƙungiyar Turai, Thorbjorn Olesen, daga Denmark.
Mafi kyawun ɗan wasan golf, Dustin Johnson, ya juya 2 da 1 a gaban Turanci Ian Poulter, wanda zai iya buga kofin Ryder na karshe.
Tsohon takwas Ryder Cup, Spain Sergio Garcia ya zama zakarun Turai na kowane lokaci tare da jimillar maki 25.5 na wasanni.
"Galibi, ba zan yi kuka ba, amma a yau ya fi ƙarfin ni.
