Abin da ya fi muhimmanci shi ne tawagar, kuma ina farin cikin taimaka masa, "in ji Garcia da damuwa bayan nasarar Turai.
Ya ba da fitila ga danginsa John Ram wanda ya lashe tarihin golf na Amurka Tiger Woods 2-1 a cikin sauki, a ranar Lahadi na karshe.
